      • deleteIfExists

        public boolean deleteIfExists(Path path)
                       throws IOException
        The default implementation in FileSystemProvider will simply call delete() in deleteIfExists() and silently ignore any NoSuchFileException. In case of Nexus, trying to delete() will result in 503 (Not allowed) even if the path points to nowhere.
